reviews.review_text: fun with the Nevilles The Neville Brothers played part of the second set.  Cool Aiko -->> Man Smart.

music never faster This may be the fastest version of music never stopped I've ever heard. While that may be why Bobby struggles twice with lyrics, Jerry rises to the challenge and gives off some delightful takes. The slight stumble as they slide back from the ending space to the ending groove quickly hits that groove with a classic forward frenzy, and the end is extended in fine form.   I was at the show on the 27th, didn't have a great time, fled the city, and came back to see the new years show from the sidelines.  This show on the 30th would have been the one to see.  They fire on all cylinders throughout.
